criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant woman over 18-year-old ;

          -  Ongoing health insurance ;

          -  Informed consent ;

          -  Prenatal samples from amniotic fluid ;

          -  Isolated congenital heart defect.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Transposition of great arteries ;

          -  Amniotic fluid sample refusal.
